<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Password reset success</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h3>Password reset success</h3>
    <p>Hi <b>{{name}}</b>, you have requested to reset your password.</p>
    <p>
        it looks like you forgot your password. Don't worry, we can help you reset it.
    </p>
